### 上传证据文件
POST http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="caseId"

1000001
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

电子合同原件
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a trusted digital evidence demo file.
--WebAppBoundary--

### 分页查询证据
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&caseId=1000001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 查询证据详情
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 查询证据 Hash
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/hash/{{evidenceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 校验证据完整性
POST http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "重新计算MinIO对象SHA-256并比对原始Hash"
}

### 获取原始文件预签名下载地址
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/download-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 生成PDF固化凭证
POST http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/seal
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "生成电子证据固化凭证"
}

### 获取PDF固化凭证下载地址
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/seal/download-url
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 查询证据链
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/chains
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 校验证据链完整性
POST http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/chains/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 查询操作日志
GET http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 冻结证据
POST http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/freeze
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "司法审查期间冻结证据"
}

### 逻辑删除证据
DELETE http://localhost:9003/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
